    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m super excited to find a new home for my car! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape, ready to hit the road with you. It drives smoothly and has been really well-cared for\u2014perfect for your next adventure. You\u2019re going to love it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
